  this is my millionth attempt at writing a bio. simply put, i&apos;m one of those fortunate few who hopped off the black-and-white, ultra-fancy big-tech treadmill to pave my own muddy but technicolor path as an entrepreneur + artist. like well-merged git branches, i combined the learnings from my tech career with my roots as a classical musician, the heart of an artistic tinkerer, and the genetics of good business to commit to the lofty dream of creating one&apos;s own career out of passion.
